we don't have.

28:12.820 --> 28:15.186
We lag behind virtually
every other major Chicago firm

28:15.220 --> 28:16.756
in diversity hiring.

28:16.790 --> 28:18.724
I'm tired of being
the poster boy

28:18.760 --> 28:19.988
for affirmative
action around here.

28:20.030 --> 28:21.827
Okay, fine.

28:21.860 --> 28:23.919
We'll find the money.

28:25.530 --> 28:26.895
All right.

28:32.870 --> 28:34.838
Now, it's your turn

28:34.880 --> 28:36.836
to do something for us.

28:36.880 --> 28:39.348
Ten other lavwers
who were gonna go with you--...

28:40.380 --> 28:42.041
...their names.

28:43.820 --> 28:46.812
What, you want me to...

