for diversity hiring.

29:02.570 --> 29:04.401
Write down the names.

29:11.180 --> 29:13.307
What is that?
The results

29:13.350 --> 29:14.544
of my questioning
the employees.

29:14.580 --> 29:15.774
One received that

29:15.820 --> 29:17.173
the week before
the attack.

29:17.220 --> 29:18.983
Tell they didn't
take this to Clay.

29:19.020 --> 29:21.284
They took
it to Clay.
And he ignored it?

29:21.320 --> 29:23.185
