had prior notice?

29:31.230 --> 29:33.369
If we know this,
Stern knows this.

29:33.400 --> 29:35.095
Oh, well, that's
a happy thought.

29:35.140 --> 29:36.835
That's me, Mr. Cheer.

29:36.870 --> 29:38.201
Well, it makes Clay's
questioning tomorrow

29:38.240 --> 29:39.901
that much more
important.

29:39.940 --> 29:41.976
