another problem.

29:42.010 --> 29:43.307
Julius was

29:43.340 --> 29:44.477
handHng
questioning.

29:44.510 --> 29:46.398
Why is that a problem?

29:46.450 --> 29:48.270
Maybe Cary
should take it.

29:48.320 --> 29:50.811
No. Alicia.

29:50.850 --> 29:53.489
She can get in
Stern's face more
effectively.

29:53.520 --> 29:54.885
(elevator bell dings)

29:57.060 --> 30:00.257
The fact is, you know something
about Stern no one else knows.

30:00.290 --> 30:01.928
I can't use it, Kalinda.

30:01.960 --> 30:03.291
You can't not use it.

30:03.330 --> 30:05.469
It violates
attorney-client
privilege.

30:05.500 --> 30:09.539
Only if you tell someone,
