31:40.030 --> 31:41.395
JONAS:
Mr. Clay,

31:41.430 --> 31:44.661
what is The
Naked Columnist?

31:44.700 --> 31:46.565
(exhales)

31:46.600 --> 31:49.034
An advice columnist
in my paper

31:49.070 --> 31:52.665
