31:57.010 --> 31:58.170
And this is America.

31:58.210 --> 31:59.370
We can handle it.

31:59.410 --> 32:02.015
The Naked... Columnist.

32:02.050 --> 32:04.018
CLAY:
There's room for
entertainment

32:04.050 --> 32:05.017
