32:27.510 --> 32:29.705
Objection!
Not in evidence.
Yes.

32:29.740 --> 32:33.506
Your Honor, this is
plaintiff's exhibit N--

32:33.550 --> 32:36.041
the police report...

32:36.080 --> 32:37.342
