33:21.100 --> 33:22.089
Mrs. Florrick?

33:22.130 --> 33:23.119
Overruled.

33:24.100 --> 33:25.567
STERN:
Thank you, Your Honor.

33:25.600 --> 33:28.091
Uh...

33:28.140 --> 33:29.630
Ugh. (laughs)

33:29.670 --> 33:31.638
Where was I?

33:31.670 --> 33:33.399
Uh, right, right.

33:33.440 --> 33:34.577
Dumbwaiter,
employees.

33:34.610 --> 33:36.134
So, Mr. Clay,

33:36.180 --> 33:37.374
have any of the employees

33:37.410 --> 33:40.049
approached you about threats
they might have been receiv...?

33:40.080 --> 33:41.069
Objection.
Overly vague.

33:41.120 --> 33:42.075
Mrs. Florrick.

33:42.120 --> 33:43.246
You're right.

33:43.280 --> 33:44.440
Withdrawn, Your Honor.

33:44.490 --> 33:47.050
