for further questions.

34:43.540 --> 34:45.303
At this time,

34:45.350 --> 34:48.148
I suggest a, uh,
a ten-minute recess.

34:53.890 --> 34:55.152
CARY:
You know
what I don't understand?

34:55.190 --> 34:56.384
