something else?

35:12.510 --> 35:13.829
Okay.

35:13.870 --> 35:15.531
I'm listening.

35:15.580 --> 35:18.105
And...

35:20.350 --> 35:21.772
That's all I got.

35:21.820 --> 35:24.789
I didn't say I was
solving something.

35:24.820 --> 35:26.481
I just said I
didn't understand.

35:29.790 --> 35:31.587
I want credit for it.

35:31.630 --> 35:33.689
Whatever you get,
I want credit.

35:33.730 --> 35:36.324
Hmm. Whatever.

35:36.360 --> 35:39.227
CARY:
Mr. Thiessen,
you covered the bombing

35:39.270 --> 35:40.419
at the Oak Lawn synagogue?

35:40.470 --> 35:41.789
That's right.
And it's

35:41.840 --> 35:42.898
your opinion
that this bomb

35:42.940 --> 35:44.635
was very similar
to that one?

35:44.670 --> 35:45.807
