35:57.220 --> 35:58.482
No, no.

35:58.520 --> 36:00.181
It was identical.

36:00.220 --> 36:02.279
CARY:
A modified flashbulb?

36:02.320 --> 36:03.514
Yes, from a camera.

36:03.560 --> 36:04.629
It's quite clever.

36:04.660 --> 36:06.582
It produces just enough flame
to trigger the fuse.

36:06.630 --> 36:08.655
CARY:
Oh, that's
interesting.

36:08.700 --> 36:10.588
But when you reported
