36:11.930 --> 36:13.864
THIESSEN:
It's kind of a
technical detail.

36:13.900 --> 36:16.562
A little beyond the scope
of a basic news article.

36:16.600 --> 36:17.760
CARY:
Of course.

36:17.800 --> 36:19.358
It's just that

36:19.410 --> 36:20.968
