36:29.720 --> 36:30.846
RACHEL:
Objection, Your Honor!

36:30.880 --> 36:32.211
JUDGE:
Objection?

36:32.250 --> 36:33.547
There hasn't been
a question yet.

36:33.590 --> 36:35.615
Overruled.

36:35.660 --> 36:37.981
