on the triggering mechanism,

36:38.020 --> 36:40.727
Mr. Thiessen,
the only person I can think of

36:40.760 --> 36:43.297
who possesses all
of that knowledge would be you.

36:43.330 --> 36:44.888
RACHEL:
Objection, Your Honor.

36:44.930 --> 36:46.818
